 ALLDISKS must be used with VOLUMEREQUEST. Example:
@{fg fill}
 VOLUMEREQUEST "Select a Device" VOLUMEREQUEST ALLDISKS
@{fg text}

     @{"VOLUMEREQUEST - ALLDISKS" SYSTEM "execute demo.rtFileRequest.8a"}
@ENDNODE

