 Installation is very simple. We recommend you make a root directory
 on your hard drive and copy the directories and files in this package
 into that root directory.

 Execute the Installer.script. This script will copy to a place of your
 choosing the executables necessary to use MUInt and DOSReqTools .

 We suggest you copy these files to a directory that is in the path.

     The name of this directory should NOT have spaces in it.

 The installer will allow you to create a new directory to hold these 
 files. If you choose to do this, you must alter your startup-sequence
 to add this directory to the path.

 The installer will create the files DOSRTPATH and MUINTPATH in Env-Archive
 so the rtMan program can find out where you put these AmigaGuide files.

