 well. We currently have compiled COMAL programs interacting with the
 requesters and MUInt perfectly. I even wrote some ACE Basic programs 
 that work with them as well.

 The executables contained in these archives are not memory hungry. 
 They have been run on A500s with minimum RAM.
 
 I *do* answer my Email, so don't hesitate to send me questions.

Colin Thompson
6-25-95
San Diego, California

